        pkg-config
Imports: graphics, stats, filearray (>= 0.1.3), Rcpp, waveslim (>=
        1.8.2), signal (>= 0.7.7), pracma, digest (>= 0.6.29), splines,
        RNiftyReg (>= 2.7.1), Rvcg (>= 0.22.1), R6 (>= 2.5.1)
